10.60	Citizen_Cyborg	Citizen Cyborg	Citizen Cyborg: Why Democratic Societies Must Respond to the Redesigned Human of the Future is a 2004 non-fiction book by bioethicist and sociologist James Hughes, which articulates democratic transhumanism as a socio-political ideology and program.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/8/80/Citizencyborg.jpg
